title: Zeit Coin Moon 1/24: Eric Clapton, Sarah Palin, Bari Weiss, Weird High School Stories, Bubbles, Kanye, Shell

description:
In this edition of Zeit Coin Moon, Jack and Miles discuss Eric Clapton claiming vaxx'd people are under hypnosis, Sarah Palin's defamation trial being delayed by COVID, Bari Weiss being 'over' COVID, weird high school stories, the numerous bubbles about to pop in the US, Kanye and Julia Fox's matching outfits, and Shell's carbon capture facility emitting more than it captures.
